		"description": "<p style=\"text-align: right\"><em>T&amp;T 315</em></p><p><strong>Crafting Components:</strong> Shell that’s been home to three different sea creatures</p><hr class=\"a5e-rule u-my-md\"><p>While wearing this charm you gain a swim speed equal to your Speed, or you can break the charm to release its power, destroying it to activate one of the following effects.</p><p>• <strong><em>Breathe</em></strong>: Cast @Compendium[a5e.a5e-spells.ibapaaz63sgen1ao]{Water Breathing}.<br>• <strong><em>Cure</em></strong>: Cast @Compendium[a5e.a5e-spells.n38oneuah7io59c9]{Cure Wounds} at 3rd-level (+3 spellcasting ability modifier).<br>• <strong><em>Numb</em></strong>: Cast @Compendium[a5e.a5e-spells.18vcyto3p7wj17cx]{Sleet Storm} (spell save DC 15).</p><p><strong>Curse</strong>. Releasing the charm’s power attracts the attention of a marid or water elemental who seeks you out to recruit you for a task. <br></p>",
